# Public QTI Certification

- Public certification coverage in this repository must use clean-room fixtures, public sample items, and the `bun run test:certification:public` gate.
- Do not copy official 1EdTech conformance ZIP/XML assets into this repository or add tests that require a private sibling checkout such as `../qti-conformance`.
- Official conformance package execution belongs in the private `pie-qti-conformance` project and must consume published `@pie-qti/*` packages.
- When changing QTI extraction, assessment delivery, response processing, MathML rendering, or browser-visible interaction behavior, update `docs/certification/public-coverage-matrix.json` and run `bun run test:certification:public`.
- Keep public CI, default build scripts, and contributor workflows runnable without private credentials or member-only assets.
